{You greet her with a smile.}
        ]

        [
        {After you join the audience, you soon fall into the illusion that the moon is rising from the back of the piano.}
{You don't think the scenery can only be described as "fantastic".}
{And as always, a keyboard for the third movement is prepared for you.}
{After the ecstasy of sitting in a seat and playing, you will only be able to realize the bitter feelings of neglect.}
