        [
       {As she plays the first movement, you close your ears, close your eyes, and ignore her.}
{It was not the piano melody that caught you but the low voice afterwards.}
{"Tales say that the moon bewitches man, yet in reality, it is the man that despairs at the moon."}
{Her performance without a smile was cut off, and no sonatas were played for you ever since.}
